lidations)\n    39→- No circular dependencies detected by madge\n    40→- No merge conflict markers in any `.ts` file\n    41→- No `.env` files containing passwords/secrets\n    42→- TypeScript strict mode enabled in all packages\n    43→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AS9M4FmgoEF2QxPxaupaXu","session_id":"e1a17e76-b4a0-403e-bbcf-50b1d69db88d","uuid":"84683a26-a281-47aa-87fb-24bf9f49597d"}
