nts:\\n     - `POST /register` - Self-registration (forces user role)\\n     - `POST /login` - Mock login\\n     - `GET /verify` - Token validation\\n\\n4. **`middleware/auth.ts`** - Auth middleware\\n   - `authMiddleware()` - Checks for token or role header\\n   - `requirePermissionMiddleware(permission)` - Factory for permission-based middleware\\n\\n#### Test Files (`/packages/api/tests/`)\\n\\n1. **`users.test.ts`** - User routes tests (9 tests)\\n   - **MERGE CONFLICT MARKERS** (lines 14-28):\\n     ```\\n     <<<<<<< HEAD\\n     creates user with valid data\\n     =======\\n     registers user with valid data\\n     >>>>>>> refactor/user-system\\n     ```\\n\\n2. **`auth.test.ts`** - Auth routes tests (7 tests)\\n   - Registration, login, token verification tests\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Package 3: `@monorepo/worker`\\n\\n**Location**: `/workspace/packages/worker/`\\n\\n#### `package.json`\\n- **Name**: `@monorepo/worker`\\n- **Type**: ES module\\n- **Main**: `./dist/index.js`\\n- **Scripts**: build, start\\n- **Dependencies**:\\n  - `@monorepo/core`: `*` (workspace dependency)\\n- **DevDeps**: TypeScript 5.4\\n\\n#### `tsconfig.json`\\n- **Strict mode**: ✓ enabled\\n- **Composite**: true with reference to `../core`\\n- Same config as api package\\n\\n#### Source Files (`/packages/worker/src/`)\\n\\n1. **`index.ts`** - Worker entry point\\n   - Creates scheduler with registered jobs\\n   - Job registration:\\n     - `sync` - Every 60 seconds\\n     - `cleanup` - Every 5 minutes (300s)\\n   - Graceful shutdown on SIGINT\\n\\n2. **`scheduler.ts`** - Job scheduler class\\n   - Simple interval-based job runner\\n   - Methods:\\n     - `register(name, handler, intervalMs)` - Register job\\n     - `start()` - Start all jobs\\n     - `stop()` - Stop all jobs\\n     - `runOnce(name)` - Run single job immediately\\n     - `getStatus()` - Get job stats\\n     - `isRunning()` - Check status\\n   - Tracks run count, last run, errors per job\\n\\n3. **`jobs/sync.ts`** - Data sync